            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>拼多多控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PDD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PDD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PDD-US</a>)截至台北時間11日00:50股價下跌6.6美元，報124.65美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量12,382,978（股），盤中最高價132.33美元、最低價124.65美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.22%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.76%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-2.45%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-4.45%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>拼多多控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PDD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PDD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PDD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-2.95%</li> <li>近 1 月：+4.12%</li> <li>近 3 月：+25%</li> <li>近 6 月：+39.66%</li> <li>今年以來：+35.32%</li></ul></section></main>",
